---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Oteria Conseil – Performance énergétique et aides CEE pour les professionnels"
  description="Cabinet de conseil en performance énergétique. Accompagnement CEE, courtage énergie et bornes IRVE pour l'industrie, le tertiaire et les collectivités."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #102a43;">
    <canvas id="network-canvas" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full opacity-[0.35]"></canvas>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 md:py-16">

      <!-- ACCROCHE : contexte avant le choix -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-9 md:mb-11">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #f5c04a;">
          19 ans d'expertise en performance énergétique
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight" style="color: #ffffff;">
          Réduisez vos coûts énergétiques.
          <br />
          <span style="color: #f5c04a;">Maximisez vos primes CEE.</span>
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- PARTIE 1/3 : trois entrées distinctes, même poids visuel -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 md:mb-10">

        <a href="/dispositifs/" class="group flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 rounded-xl p-4 no-underline border transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(245, 192, 74, 0.25);">
          <div class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" style="background-color: rgba(245, 192, 74, 0.15);">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" style="color: #f5c04a;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 0 0 8.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 0 1-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 0 1 7.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 0 0-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0 1 12 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0 1 21 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m-15.432 0A8.959 8.959 0 0 1 3 12c0-.778.099-1.533.284-2.253" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #ffffff; font-family: var(--font-heading);">Découverte de l'univers CEE</p>
            <p class="text-xs mt-1" style="color: #9fb3c8;">Comprendre le dispositif, les primes et les démarches</p>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #f5c04a;">
            Explorer
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/dispositifs/comprendre-les-cee/" class="group flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 rounded-xl p-4 no-underline border transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-color: rgba(245, 192, 74, 0.25);">
          <div class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" style="background-color: rgba(245, 192, 74, 0.15);">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" style="color: #f5c04a;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #ffffff; font-family: var(--font-heading);">Fiches d'opérations standardisées</p>
            <p class="text-xs mt-1" style="color: #9fb3c8;">Consultez directement les fiches CEE par opération</p>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold" style="color: #f5c04a;">
            Consulter
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <div class="rounded-xl p-4 shadow-xl bg-white">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2.5" style="color: #7a530d;">Vous êtes&nbsp;?</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3.5">
            <a href="/diagnostic-gratuit/" class="group relative flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl p-2.5 no-underline transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg" style="background-color: #102a43;">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" style="background-color: rgba(245, 192, 74, 0.15);">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4" style="color: #f5c04a;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 21h16.5M4.5 3h15M5.25 3v18m13.5-18v18M9 6.75h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m3-6H15m-1.5 3H15m-1.5 3H15M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: #ffffff; font-family: var(--font-heading);">Je suis bénéficiaire</p>
                <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #9fb3c8;">Audit de votre gisement CEE</p>
              </div>
              <svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" style="color: #f5c04a;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
              </svg>
            </a>

            <a href="/contact-installateur/" class="group relative flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl p-2.5 no-underline border-2 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:bg-navy-50" style="border-color: #102a43;">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" style="background-color: #f0f4f8;">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-navy-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17 17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0 0 21 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 1 1-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 0 1-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085m-1.745 1.437L5.909 7.5H4.5L2.25 3.75l1.5-1.5L7.5 4.5v1.409l4.26 4.26m-1.745 1.437 1.745-1.437m6.615 8.206L15.75 15.75M4.867 19.125h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-navy-900" style="font-family: var(--font-heading);">Je suis installateur</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-navy-600 mt-0.5">Rejoindre notre réseau</p>
              </div>
              <svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 text-navy-400 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:text-gold-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SUITE DU CONTENU HERO : paragraphe + citation, sous les trois entrées -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #d9e2ec;">
          Oteria Conseil accompagne les professionnels dans l'optimisation de leur performance
          énergétique grâce au dispositif des certificats d'économie d'énergie (CEE).
        </p>

        <blockquote class="founders-quote relative mt-5 pl-10 border-l-2" style="border-color: #d4a024;">
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base italic leading-relaxed" style="color: #f0f4f8; font-family: var(--font-heading);">
            « Nous avons négocié les premiers CEE, nous connaissons le potentiel du dispositif et ses moindres contours. »
          </p>
          <footer class="mt-2.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: #f5c04a;">
            Le mot des fondateurs
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INDICATEURS DE CONFIANCE -->
  <section class="border-b border-navy-100 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900" style="font-family: var(--font-heading)">19 ans</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">D'expertise CEE</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900" style="font-family: var(--font-heading)">14M€</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">De primes CEE obtenues</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900" style="font-family: var(--font-heading)">30%</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">D'économies moyennes</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900" style="font-family: var(--font-heading)">48h</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 mt-1">Délai de réponse</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPERTISES -->
  <section class="bg-navy-50 py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #7a530d;">Nos domaines d'intervention</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900">Des expertises concrètes, des résultats mesurables</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <a href="/expertises/destratificateur/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Destratificateurs</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Réduction de 20 à 30 % du chauffage par homogénéisation thermique. Prime CEE incluse.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/expertises/vmc-double-flux/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 4.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 1.332-7.257 3 3 0 0 0-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 0 0-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 0 0 2.25 15Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">VMC double flux</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Ventilation haut rendement avec récupération de chaleur. Aide CEE et dimensionnement.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/expertises/variateur-de-vitesse/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.594 3.94c.09-.542.56-.94 1.11-.94h2.593c.55 0 1.02.398 1.11.94l.213 1.281c.063.374.313.686.645.87.074.04.147.083.22.127.325.196.72.257 1.075.124l1.217-.456a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 1.37.49l1.296 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-.26 1.431l-1.003.827c-.293.241-.438.613-.43.992a7.723 7.723 0 0 1 0 .255c-.008.378.137.75.43.991l1.004.827c.424.35.534.955.26 1.43l-1.298 2.247a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.369.491l-1.217-.456c-.355-.133-.75-.072-1.076.124a6.47 6.47 0 0 1-.22.128c-.331.183-.581.495-.644.869l-.213 1.281c-.09.543-.56.94-1.11.94h-2.594c-.55 0-1.019-.398-1.11-.94l-.213-1.281c-.062-.374-.312-.686-.644-.87a6.52 6.52 0 0 1-.22-.127c-.325-.196-.72-.257-1.076-.124l-1.217.456a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.369-.49l-1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 .26-1.431l1.004-.827c.292-.24.437-.613.43-.991a6.932 6.932 0 0 1 0-.255c.007-.38-.138-.751-.43-.992l-1.004-.827a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-.26-1.43l1.297-2.247a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 1.37-.491l1.216.456c.356.133.751.072 1.076-.124.072-.044.146-.086.22-.128.332-.183.582-.495.644-.869l.214-1.28Z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Variateurs de vitesse</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Régulation des moteurs électriques. Économies de 20 à 50 % sur les pompes et ventilateurs.</p>
        </a>
        <div class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m3.75 13.5 10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Bornes IRVE</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Installation de bornes de recharge pour entreprises, copropriétés et collectivités.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/expertises/pompe-a-chaleur/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.362 5.214A8.252 8.252 0 0 1 12 21 8.25 8.25 0 0 1 6.038 7.048 8.287 8.287 0 0 0 9 9.6a8.983 8.983 0 0 1 3.361-6.867 8.21 8.21 0 0 0 3 2.48Z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 .495-7.467 5.99 5.99 0 0 0-1.925 3.546 5.974 5.974 0 0 1-2.133-1A3.75 3.75 0 0 0 12 18Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Pompe à chaleur</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Solutions air-eau, géothermie et DRV pour le tertiaire. Financement CEE et étude COP/SCOP.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/expertises/isolation-thermique/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205 3 1.091M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636 10.5-3.819" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Isolation thermique</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">ITE, combles et planchers bas pour bâtiments tertiaires et industriels. Primes CEE en 6e période.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/expertises/air-comprime/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75m-16.5-3.75v3.75m16.5 0v3.75C20.25 16.153 16.556 18 12 18s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Air comprimé</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Optimisation des installations industrielles, détection de fuites. Réduction de 20 à 40 % des coûts.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/expertises/gtb-gtc/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 6h9.75M10.5 6a1.5 1.5 0 1 1-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 1 0-3 0M3.75 6H7.5m3 12h9.75m-9.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-3 0m-3.75 0H7.5m9-6h3.75m-3.75 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-3 0m-9.75 0h9.75" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">GTB / GTC</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Pilotage centralisé du bâtiment, conformité décret BACS. Économies de 15 à 30 % et prime CEE.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/expertises/hp-bp-flottante/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 7.5 7.5 3m0 0L12 7.5M7.5 3v13.5m13.5 0L16.5 21m0 0L12 16.5m4.5 4.5V7.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">HP/BP flottante</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Optimisation des pressions frigorifiques : 15 à 30 % d'économies sur les installations de froid industriel et commercial.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMMENT ÇA MARCHE -->
